Sentencas: A bio-inspired surfactant was utilized to assist in the efficient impregnation of a nano-CeO2 catalyst throughout both porous Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFC's) electrodes simultaneously.
Titulo: Bio-inspired surfactant assisted nano-catalyst impregnation of Solid-Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) electrodes

Sentencas: The process included the initial modification of electrode pore walls with a polydopamine film.
Titulo: Bio-inspired surfactant assisted nano-catalyst impregnation of Solid-Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) electrodes

Sentencas: The cell was then submersed into a cerium salt solution.
Titulo: Bio-inspired surfactant assisted nano-catalyst impregnation of Solid-Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) electrodes

Sentencas: The amount of nano-CeO2 deposited per impregnation step increased by 3.5 times by utilizing this two-step protocol in comparison to a conventional drip impregnation method.
Titulo: Bio-inspired surfactant assisted nano-catalyst impregnation of Solid-Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) electrodes

Sentencas: The impregnated cells exhibited a 20% higher power density than a baseline cell without the nanocatalyst at 750 degrees C (using humid H-2 fuel).
Titulo: Bio-inspired surfactant assisted nano-catalyst impregnation of Solid-Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) electrodes
